author: enridaga
msg: Actions taken in this commit is described in STANBOL-177.

This includes the patch updloaded by Alberto Musetti, with the changes of the code to support OWLApi 2.3.2 (related also to STANBOL-24, since this version is the first dual-licensed LGPL and Apache) and several improvements in the web interface of ontonet and reasoners modules.
Includes also changes in the owl-link and hermit versions.
OWLApi, Hermit and OWLLink are provided by embedded maven repositories in the 'owl', 'reasoners/hermit' and 'reasoners/owllink' modules respectively.
